source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SEQ_00<tab>Teteroon has places for you to go and thingies for you to get.
target: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SEQ_00<tab>An Memeroons Handelsposten möchte dich Teteroon bitten, Dinge für ihn zu sammeln.

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SEQ_01<tab>Teteroon has asked that you help him brew Qiqirn firewater. To do so, slay coeurl pups to obtain three coeurl pup whiskers.
target: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SEQ_01<tab>Du sollst Teteroon dabei helfen, <var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E86D20A /var> herzustellen. Erlege dafür <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 061D030502 /var>, um drei <var 32 ((EventItem)) 06F61E9041030502 /var> zu sammeln.

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SEQ_02<tab>You have procured the required ingredients. Take them back to Teteroon.
target: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SEQ_02<tab>Bring die gesammelten Zutaten zu Teteroon an Memeroons Handelsposten.

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SEQ_03<tab>Teteroon has set about brewing his Qiqirn firewater from the ingredients you have provided. But good firewater takes time. Speak to him again later to learn how his concoction turns out.
target: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SEQ_03<tab>Mit den von dir gesammelten Zutaten macht sich Teteroon sofort an die Arbeit. Es dauert aber ein bisschen, bis <var 32 ((EventItem)) 03F61E86D2020202 /var> fertig gebraut ist, also sollst du später wiederkommen.

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TODO_00<tab>Slay coeurl pups and collect coeurl pup whiskers.
TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the coeurl pup whiskers to Teteroon.
TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SYSTEM_100_000<tab>To accept this quest, you must abandon the current main scenario quest. Open the corresponding entry in the journal or duty list and select “Abandon.”
target: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_SYSTEM_100_000<tab>Um diesen Auftrag annehmen zu können, muss der aktuelle Auftrag des Hauptszenarios abgebrochen werden. Öffne dazu das Archiv (Hauptmenü → Spielinhalte).

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_000<tab>Good Buscaroon help Teteroon. Teteroon dead without good Buscaroon. Must give thankies. Many, many thankies. Teteroon make Qiqirn firewater for Buscaroon! Buscaroon love firewater!
target: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_000<tab>Guter Buscarron haben Teteroon Gutes getan. Ohne guter Buscarron kein Teteroon. Teteroon muss Buscarron Gutes tun. Teteroon machen <var 32 ((EventItem)) 06F61E86D2020502 /var> für Buscarron. Guter Buscarron lieben <var 32 ((EventItem)) 06F61E86D2020502 /var>.

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_001<tab>You help Teteroon make firewater? Need thingies to make. Need many, many thingies.
target: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_001<tab>Helfen Teteroon machen Feuerwasser, ja? Teteroon brauchen Dinge. Viele Dinge, ja?

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_002<tab>Need coeurl pup whiskers. Need three good coeurl pup whiskers.
target: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_002<tab>Teteroon brauchen gutes Wasser. Geht selbst gutes Wasser suchen, ja. Aber Teteroon brauchen auch drei <var 32 ((EventItem)) 06F61E9041030502 /var> von <var 32 ((BNpcName)) 061D030502 /var>. Du holen, ja?

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_020<tab>Teteroon make firewater for Buscaroon. You bring thingies Teteroon need?
target: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_020<tab>Teteroon machen Feuerwasser für Buscarron. Du bringen Teteroon dafür Dinge, ja?

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_021<tab>You brought all thingies! Teteroon make firewater now. Make good firewater for good Buscaroon.
target: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_021<tab>Du hast alle Dinge geholt! Teteroon machen jetzt Feuerwasser. Gutes Feuerwasser für guten Buscarron.

source: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_022<tab>Teteroon start making firewater now. Good firewater take time. More time, more good. You come back later.
target: TEXT_XXAUSA302_03861_TETEROON_000_022<tab>Gutes Feuerwasser brauchen Zeit. Mehr Zeit, mehr gut. Kommen später wieder, ja?
